query:
SELECT t.id, t.companyId, t.followers, c.id as company_id, c.name as company_name 
FROM tiktokMetrics t 
LEFT JOIN companies c ON t.companyId = c.id 
ORDER BY t.createdAt DESC LIMIT 5
